snippet.title: Indie 2D MMORPG: Wizbirds Online Teaser
snippet.description:
PLAY NOW: https://firith.itch.io/wizbirds-online

Wizbirds Online is a free to play 2D Side-scrolling MMORPG where you can meet new players! Fight fiesty mobs, collect cool hats, and level up your stats. Wizbirds Online is a free-to-play massively multiplayer role-playing game by Firith Studio.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Want to help support us with further development?
